sql:

    p.abstract,
    p.venue,

    p.citation_count
FROM Papers p

    (
        p.venue ILIKE '%acm sigchi conference on human factors in computing systems%'
        OR p.venue ILIKE '%chi%'
    )
    AND (
        (p.title || ' ' || COALESCE(p.abstract, '')) ILIKE '%video game%'
        OR (p.title || ' ' || COALESCE(p.abstract, '')) ILIKE '%video games%'
        OR (p.title || ' ' || COALESCE(p.abstract, '')) ILIKE '%game play%'

    )
    AND (p.title || ' ' || COALESCE(p.abstract, '')) ILIKE '%grounded%'
ORDER BY
    -- prioritize exact venue match, then more keyword hits, then citations
    (CASE
        WHEN p.venue ILIKE '%acm sigchi conference on human factors in computing systems%' THEN 3
        WHEN p.venue ILIKE '%chi%' THEN 2
        ELSE 0
     END) DESC,
    (
        (CASE WHEN (p.title || ' ' || COALESCE(p.abstract, '')) ILIKE '%video game%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) +
        (CASE WHEN (p.title || ' ' || COALESCE(p.abstract, '')) ILIKE '%video games%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) +
        (CASE WHEN (p.title || ' ' || COALESCE(p.abstract, '')) ILIKE '%game play%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) +
